PROGRAM 1 : Write a program to print the following pattern

****
***
**
*

CODE :

import java.util.Scanner;
public class Loops{
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        for(int i=4 ; i>=1 ; i--){
            for(int j=1;j<=i; j++){
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println("\n");
        }
    }
}
